sections.heading: Kerosene; delivery; container or portable tank prohibited
sections.text: No person shall deliver kerosene, or what is known as coal oil, in any container or portable tank painted or stamped as provided by section 66-103.SourceLaws 1907, c. 86, ยง 2, p. 305;R.S.1913, ยง 5755;C.S.1922, ยง 5100;C.S.1929, ยง 66-104;R.S.19
